data.description: VACANT EASY SHOW. CHECK VIRTUAL TOUR. Introducing an exceptional 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom single-family home, nestled in the highly desirable Deltona Lakes neighborhood. This residence is truly a standout, featuring a beautifully fenced yard that encloses a private swimming pool, along with a convenient 2-car garage. The exterior boasts an inviting, bright finish that radiates curb appeal, welcoming you home each day. Step inside, and you'll immediately appreciate the open floor plan, enhanced by elegant laminate flooring that seamlessly connects the living spaces. An entryway closet adds a touch of practicality to your daily routine, while vaulted ceilings and double-hung windows flood the home with natural light. An archway gracefully links the living room to the tiled kitchen, a culinary haven equipped with top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, a thoughtfully designed built-in pantry, abundant wooden cabinets, and a functional kitchen peninsula. The stainless steel double sink, complete with a pull-out faucet, not only enhances functionality but also complements the modern appliances seamlessly. Accessibility from both the garage and laundry area makes this kitchen incredibly convenient for daily living. The master bedroom is a true retreat, offering not just one but two walk-in closets to meet all your storage needs. The first walk-in closet, conveniently located within the master bathroom, is perfect for keeping your essentials organized and within easy reach. The master bedroom is complete with an ensuite bathroom and a second walk-in closet adorned with charming archways. The master bathroom is a spa-like oasis, boasting a luxurious garden tub, a private water closet, and a standing shower with beautifully tiled, height-level walls. The single vanity features an oversized framed mirror, ample cabinets for storage, and contemporary bar lights.  Two additional bedrooms come equipped with built-in closets and share a well-appointed bathroom, featuring a shower and tub combination with elegant height-level tiling, a vanity enhanced by an oversized framed mirror, and tastefully chosen bar lights.  Step through the glass sliding door from the living area, and you'll find yourself on a screened porch, providing the perfect space for enjoying the outdoors without any pesky bugs. Beyond the porch, a screened-in private swimming pool awaits, surrounded by a spacious fenced backyard that's ideal for entertaining and various outdoor activities. Strategically situated at the intersection of I-4 and Saxon Blvd, this charming home is ideally located in Deltona, offering easy access to numerous shopping areas, fitness centers, and an array of excellent dining options. Whether you're yearning for the vibrant atmosphere of downtown Orlando or the sandy shores of Daytona Beach, you're just a short drive away with quick access to the I-4 highway. In a mere 25 minutes, you can find yourself in the heart of downtown Orlando, and in under an hour, you can reach Daytona and New Smyrna Beaches, as well as popular attractions like Downtown Disney, Seaworld, and Universal Studios. Embrace the vibrant Florida lifestyle in this inviting single-family home – your new home awaits! Schedule your private tour today and experience the convenience and excitement this location has to offer.  <iframe width='853' height='480' src='https://my.matterport.com/show/?m=ZApQ6TXsMpE&mls=1' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen allow='xr-spatial-tracking'></iframe>
